Description: Computes multivariate normal and t probabilities, quantiles,
  random deviates, and densities. Interval-censored log-likelihoods for Gaussian 
  copulae parameterised by Cholesky factors of covariance matrices are implemented 
  in addition. Methods for a class representing multiple lower triangular matrices 
  are available.
Imports: stats, methods
Depends: R(>= 3.5.0)
Suggests: qrng, numDeriv
License: GPL-2
URL: http://mvtnorm.R-forge.R-project.org
